trend_summary: Between earliest and latest images, suburban township shows steady infill housing, new commercial nodes along highways, and gradual farmland loss. Forest cover declines slightly yet remains extensive; road network thickens with new connectors. Growth is moderate, producing a continuous but still green mosaic without high-rise cores.
